(9, 7, 'Cougar Case DarkBlader X5 White | DARKBL', '685d9efd9678a4.95197757.png', 'Distinctive Mid-Tower Case with Superior Airflow<br>Cooling Fan Support Front * 120mm x 3 / 140mm x 3<br>Top 120mm x 3 / 140mm x 2<br>Rear 120mm ( pre-installed )<br>Maximun Number of Fans 7 Max.<br>Water Cooling Support Front *360mm / 280mm / 240mm / 140mm / 120mm<br>Top *360mm / 280mm / 240mm / 140mm / 120mm<br>Rear 120mm<br>Transparent Left Panel 4mm Tempered Glass<br>Max. Graphics Card Length 400 (mm) / 15.7 (in)<br>(Horizontal graphics card slots are compatible with RTX 3090/3080/3070.)<br>Max. CPU Cooler Height 170 (mm) / 6.7 (in)</p>\r\n', 90),
(14, 13, 'Kisonli A-909 Wired Computer Speaker - R', '685eb02094ca98.96064265.webp', 'Computer speakers\r\nAUX\r\nOutput power - 2x3W\r\nImpedance - 4 Ohm\r\nFrequency response -  20 Hz-20 KHz\r\nPower supply - USB - 5V\r\nColor - Black', 7),
(15, 1, 'AMD Ryzen 9 7950X CPU Desktop Processor ', '685eb531cbb9b7.62894787.jpg', 'Processor consumes less power to offer maximum productivity with added usability\r\nRyzen 9 product line processor for better usability and increased efficiency from expert zone\r\n5 nm process technology provides optimal processing results with added usability\r\nHexadeca-core (16 Core) processor core efficiently handles data to ensure quicker transfer of information with maximum usability\r\n16 MB L2 plus 64 MB L3 cache memory provides excellent hit rate in short access time enabling improved system performance\r\nProcessor with 4.50 GHz clock speed for quick and dependable processing of data to ensure maximum productivity\r\nComes with AMD Radeon Graphics controller for stunning picture quality', 399),
(16, 1, 'AMD Ryzen 7 9700X – CPU Ryzen 7 9000 Ser', '685eb579581ea4.92228921.webp', 'This high-performance gaming processor offers impressive 100+ FPS speeds in the world’s top games.\r\nIt features 8 cores and 16 threads built on AMD’s “Zen 5” architecture, with a max boost clock of 5.5 GHz.\r\nThe processor comes unlocked for overclocking, includes a 40 MB cache, and supports DDR5-5600 memory.\r\nDesigned for the advanced Socket AM5 platform, it is compatible with PCIe 5.0 on select motherboards.', 250),
(17, 1, 'Intel Core i3-12100 12th Generation Proc', '685eb60eaf03e2.00080886.webp', 'The Intel Core i3-12100 is a 12th Generation Alder Lake processor, designed for entry-level gaming, productivity, and everyday computing. With 4 Performance cores and 8 threads, it delivers a solid balance of efficiency and performance. The base clock of 3.3 GHz and turbo boost up to 4.3 GHz ensure fast processing speeds for daily tasks and gaming at 1080p. Supporting DDR5 memory and PCIe 5.0, this processor offers modern features at an affordable price. The tray version does not include a stock cooler, making it ideal for users planning a custom cooling setup.', 82),
(18, 1, 'Intel Core i5-14400 Processor | 14400', '685eb6449e8f88.66095140.webp', '10 cores (6 Performance-cores + 4 Efficient-cores), 16 threads\r\nBase clock: 2.5 GHz (P-cores), up to 4.7 GHz Turbo\r\nIntel Smart Cache: 20 MB\r\nProcessor Base Power: 65W\r\nSocket: LGA1700\r\nMemory support: DDR5-4800 / DDR4-3200, up to 192 GB\r\nIntegrated Graphics: Intel UHD Graphics 730\r\nPCIe 5.0 and 4.0 support', 119),
(19, 1, 'Intel Core i9-14900K LGA 1700 Processor ', '685eb72acdefc6.92150205.webp', '24 Cores & 32 Threads\r\n3.2 GHz P-Core Clock Speed\r\n5.8 GHz Maximum Turbo Boost Frequency\r\nLGA 1700 Socket\r\n36MB Cache Memory\r\nDual-Channel DDR5-5600 ECC Memory\r\nIntegrated Intel UHD 770 Graphics\r\nHybrid Core Architecture\r\nUnlocked for Overclocking\r\n14th Generation', 390),
(20, 1, 'Intel Core Ultra 5 245K Desktop Processo', '685eb9421e6341.72442379.webp', 'Get ultra-efficient with Intel Core Ultra desktop processors that improve both performance and efficiency so your PC can run cooler, quieter, and quicker.\r\nCore & Threads 14 cores (6 P-cores + 8 E-cores) and 14 threads\r\nPerformance Hybrid Architecture Integrates two core microarchitectures, prioritizing and distributing workloads to optimize performance\r\nPerformance Unlocked Up to 5.2 GHz unlocked. 26M Cache\r\nCompatibility Compatible with Intel 800 series chipset-based motherboards\r\nPCIe Express Version Turbo Boost Max Technology 3.0, and PCIe 5.0 & 4.0 support. Intel Optane Memory support. No thermal solution included', 620),
(21, 1, 'Intel Core Ultra 5 245K Desktop Processo', '685eb9e7024fe2.51068592.webp', 'The Intel Core Ultra 5 245K is a high-performance desktop processor featuring 14 cores (6 Performance-cores and 8 Efficient-cores) and 14 threads. It operates with a base clock speed of 4.2 GHz and can achieve a maximum turbo boost frequency of 5.2 GHz. The processor is built on Intels Arrow Lake architecture and utilizes the LGA 1851 socket. It includes 24 MB of Intel Smart Cache and supports up to 192 GB of DDR5 memory across two channels. The Core Ultra 5 245K is unlocked for overclocking and has a processor base power of 125 W, with a maximum turbo power of 159 W. Additionally, it features integrated Intel Xe LPG graphics.', 270),
(22, 1, 'Intel Ultra 7 265k Desktop Processor - B', '685eba2817e6f2.34834615.webp', 'Get ultra-efficient with Intel Core Ultra desktop processors that improve both performance and efficiency so your PC can run cooler, quieter, and quicker.\r\nCore & Threads 20 cores (8 P-cores + 12 E-cores) and 20 threads\r\nPerformance Hybrid Architecture Integrates two core microarchitectures, prioritizing and distributing workloads to optimize performance\r\nPerformance Unlocked Up to 5.5 GHz unlocked. 36MB Cache\r\nCompatibility Compatible with Intel 800 series chipset-based motherboards\r\nPCIe Express Version Turbo Boost Max Technology 3.0, and PCIe 5.0 & 4.0 support. Intel Optane Memory support. No thermal solution included', 290),
(23, 1, 'Intel Ultra 9 285K Desktop Processor - T', '685eba98411c19.37899385.webp', 'Get ultra-efficient with Intel Core Ultra desktop processors that improve both performance and efficiency so your PC can run cooler, quieter, and quicker.\r\nCore & Threads 24 cores (8 P-cores + 16 E-cores) and 24 threads. Integrated Intel Graphics included\r\nPerformance Hybrid Architecture Integrates two core microarchitectures, prioritizing and distributing workloads to optimize performance\r\nPerformance Unlocked Up to 5.7 GHz unlocked. 40MB Cache\r\nCompatibility Compatible with Intel 800 series chipset-based motherboards\r\nPCIe Express Version Turbo Boost Max Technology 3.0, and PCIe 5.0 & 4.0 support. Intel Optane Memory support. No thermal solution included', 500),
